<div class="NavFrame collapsed" style="border:none;padding:0"><div class="NavHead" style="font-size:105%;background:transparent;text-align:left">Law of <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Consecrated_life" title="Consecrated life">consecrated life</a></div><div class="NavContent" style="font-size:105%;padding:0.2em 0 0.4em;text-align:center;text-align:left">
